    {
      "note_no": "5775",
      "note": "Cf. 2:245, and n. 276, where the meaning of \"a Beautiful Loan\" is explained.<br/>See also 57:18. The \"Beautiful Loan\" should be that of our own souls. We should expect no returns in kind, for that is not possible. But the reward we shall find with Allah will be infinitely greater and nobler. Cf. the biblical phrase, \"Lay up for yourselves treasures in heaven\" (Matt. vi. 20)."
